This paper discusses the malicious use of micro-task marketplaces and the need for detecting and preventing such activities. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computer Security (cs.CR), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Social Computing (cs.SOC), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
